name: Naturally Exfoliating Toner 8oz
description: Gently exfoliates with a balanced combination of glycolic acid and enzyme-rich papaya and orange extracts. Gently refreshes skin without stripping it of its moisture balance. Ingredients: Aqua, Glycerin, Propylene Glycol, Lactic Acid, Malic Acid, Glycolic Acid, Carica Papaya (Papaya) Fruit Extract, Ananas Sativus (Pineapple) Fruit Extract, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Fruit Extract, Rosa Damascena (Rose) Flower Water, Aminomethyl Propanediol, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate
